            <title>[SUREFIRE-1036] Tests using MockitoJUnitRunner are always run regardless of membership in specified group</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SUREFIRE-1036</link>
                <project id="12317927" key="SUREFIRE">Maven Surefire (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Not sure where this bug lies (junit, mockito, or failsafe) but I am trying to setup failsafe to run only tests annotated with @Category(IntegrationTest.class). It is running all of those tests PLUS any tests that use MockitoJUnitRunner regardless of whether they fall in that Category or not. Attached is a small sample project that illustrates the problem.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Windows&lt;br/&gt;
Maven 2.2.1&lt;br/&gt;
jdk1.6.0_43&lt;br/&gt;
junit 4.11&lt;br/&gt;
mockito 1.8.1</environment>
